---
---
<section id="how-it-works" class="bg-white py-20">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-5xl">

    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">
        Three levers. One system. More booked jobs.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        We install all three — you just answer the phone when it rings.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-6">

      <!-- Lever 1 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border-2 border-orange-200 p-8 md:p-10">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-5">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-orange-100 flex items-center justify-center text-orange-600 font-bold text-xl">1</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Missed-Call Protection</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Instant SMS within seconds of a missed call. Keeps the conversation alive, answers questions, and automatically guides the lead toward booking. Captures and converts missed calls directly into your calendar.
            </p>
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-orange-700 bg-orange-50 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md">
              Goal: Recover lost leads automatically, 24/7
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Lever 2 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-8 md:p-10">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-5">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center text-blue-700 font-bold text-xl">2</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Show-Up Optimization</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Pre-appointment emails and SMS reminders at 24 hours and 2 hours before each job. No more driving to a house with nobody home.
            </p>
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-blue-700 bg-blue-50 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md">
              Goal: Reduce no-shows by up to 33%
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Bonus -->
      <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-xl border border-green-200 p-8 md:p-10">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-5">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-green-100 flex items-center justify-center text-green-700 font-bold text-lg">🎁</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Bonus — Past Client Reactivation</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              One-time outreach to your past client list via email and SMS with a small free offer to get them back through the door — so you can upsell on-site.
            </p>
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-green-700 bg-green-100 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md">
              Goal: Generate quick revenue wins in the first 30 days
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Pricing box -->
    <div class="mt-14 bg-gray-900 text-white rounded-xl p-8 md:p-10 text-center">
      <div class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">All-in monthly</div>
      <div class="text-5xl font-bold mb-2">$1,000<span class="text-xl font-normal text-gray-400">/mo</span></div>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mb-6">Monthly reporting on leads recovered, calls captured, and revenue impact.</p>
      <a href="/apply" class="inline-flex px-8 py-3.5 rounded-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 bg-white hover:bg-gray-100 transition">
        Check If You Qualify →
      </a>
      <div class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-green-400 font-medium bg-green-400/10 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/></svg>
        Revenue Recovery Guarantee: 5 recovered leads booked in 30 days — or your money back.
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>